               in the opposite direction by half its own width.
               Works for images that are larger than their containers. */
            position: relative;
            left: 50%;
            display: block;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 0;
            width: 100%; /* expand with to image + margins */
            height: auto;
            transform: translateX(-50%);

